metadata.name: GAMA GATE #1 || BY BAVUGAR
metadata.description:
GAMA GATE || is one of the 4 gates of Geilen City to enter the city, a red line for strangers and untrusted, a green line for trusted residence of the city and believers of the System, artificial foggy weather, big prime head sculptures, sky scrapers, super strict check points and guarded by the PRIME guards.

If one of the PRIME guards catch a stranger trying to enter the city through the Green line they will be immediately taken down and sentenced to death, during the time that Geilen city takes place any suspicious activity is considered as a first level crime, many strict law been made by RANDAL a bloodline clone of prime father, after she over thrown the Prime Council that got co-founded by her grand grand father hundreds of years ago, all of these laws been made so she can prevent any body from harming her and her power, people are mad and scared of her, but she will do anything it takes to stay where she is even if it takes feeding people to her artificial tiger EGO THE PET...

to be continued ||
